            <div class="entry-problem"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;">ㄱ~ㅁ의 밑줄 친 단어 중, 상징의 예로 적절한 것만을 <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:black;">모두</span> 고르면?</p><div class="para0"><table style="border-collapse:collapse;width:264px;margin:3px 3px 3px 3px;" class="itex_example_tb"><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px solid black; border-collapse:collapse; width:5px; height:8pt"></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="2" style="border:none; border-collapse:collapse; width:70px; height:15pt; vertical-align:middle;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:Center;"><span style="font-size:10pt;">&lt;보기&gt;</span></p></td><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px solid black; border-collapse:collapse; height:8pt"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px solid black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; height:5pt"></td><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px solid black;border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; height:5pt"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px solid black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; width:9pt; height:19pt"></td><td colspan="3" rowspan="1" style="border:none; border-collapse:collapse; height:19pt; vertical-align:middle;"><div class="itex_box_body" data-table-title="보기"><div class="itex_box_element"><p class="para0">ㄱ. 꽃잎이 번지면 당신께도 새로운 <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:black;">봄</span>이 오겠죠.</p></div><div class="itex_box_element"><p class="para0">ㄴ. 비 내리는 여름날에 내 가슴은 <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:black;">우산</span>이 되고.</p></div><div class="itex_box_element"><p class="para0">ㄷ. 네 맘을 밝혀주는 너의 작은 별 너는 나의 <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:black;">지구</span>.</p></div><div class="itex_box_element"><p class="para0">ㄹ. 너에게 난 해 질 녘 <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:black;">노을</span>처럼 한 편의 아름다운 추억이 되고.</p></div><div class="itex_box_element"><p class="para0">ㅁ. 이 밤 그날의 <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:black;">반딧불</span>을 당신의 창 가까이 보낼게요. 사랑한다는 말이에요.</p></div></div></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px solid black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; width:9pt; height:19pt"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="5" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px solid black;border-right:1px solid black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px solid black; border-collapse:collapse; height:6pt"></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="level4"><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">① </span>ㄱ, ㄷ</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">② </span>ㄱ, ㅁ</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">③ </span>ㄴ, ㄹ</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">④ </span>ㄴ, ㅁ</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">⑤ </span>ㄷ, ㄹ</p></div></div></div>
